text: show ad Back to work! Malia Obama enjoys a weekend coffee break before heading back in for a second week of work at the Weinstein Company The first daughter headed back in for her second week of work at the Weinstein Co. on Monday Malia spent the weekend catching up with a friend and getting coffee The 18-year-old daughter of former President Obama is currently on a gap year She plans to start at Harvard in the fall and is interested in filmmaking Published: 16:30 GMT, 6 February 2017 | Updated: 19:35 GMT, 6 February 2017 108 shares
